sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as Postgres DB
    participant S3 as MinIO (S3)
    participant Q as Redis Queue
    participant W as Celery Worker
    participant B as Blender (Headless)

    Note over U, API: 1. Asset Upload
    U->>API: POST /assets/upload (File)
    API->>S3: Upload Raw File (stream)
    S3-->>API: Success (S3 Key)
    API->>DB: Create Asset (Status: PENDING)
    API->>Q: Enqueue Task (process_asset)
    API-->>U: Return Asset ID (PENDING)

    Note over W: 2. Async Processing
    W->>Q: Pop Task
    W->>DB: Update Status: PROCESSING
    W->>S3: Download Raw File
    
    W->>W: Extract Zip (if needed) & Detect Main File
    
    W->>B: Execute process_model.py
    activate B
    B->>B: Validate Geometry
    B->>B: Fix Textures & Materials
    B->>B: Normalize (Scale/Center)
    B->>B: Export to GLB
    B-->>W: Return Success/Error
    deactivate B

    W->>S3: Upload Processed GLB
    W->>DB: Update Status: COMPLETED
    W->>DB: Save Metadata (Polycount, etc)

    Note over U, S3: 3. View Result
    U->>API: GET /assets/{id}
    API->>S3: Generate Presigned URL
    API-->>U: Return URL
    U->>S3: Download GLB
